snippet.title: Short Legacy Demo
snippet.description:
Very early build demo of running around and progress made.

A newer version of this is available to try out. Still in early development version 0.2.0. You can download it here: https://firedanger.itch.io/legacy

Also you can join our Discord for more info and updates.

https://discord.gg/NhT6XbK
